msgstr "使用（Us）"

#: frontend/components/Admin/Index/CpuStatsHelpModal.vue:63
msgid "The current CPU usage including I/O Wait and Steal."
msgstr "当前 CPU 占用率，包括 I/O 等待时长和偷窃时长。"

