msgstr "Stereo Tool 许可证密钥"

#: frontend/components/Admin/Stations/Form/BackendForm.vue:190
msgid "Provide a valid license key from Thimeo. Functionality is limited without a license key."
msgstr "提供来自 Thimeo 的有效许可证密钥。没有许可证密钥，功能将受到限制。"

